How to use WELLFIT smart treadmill 

1、WELLFIT treadmill link: https://www.uswellfit.com/treamill.html
WELLFIT Treadmill info: Brand Name: WELLFIT, Model Number: WFTM014, Product Name:WFTM014 2 in 1 treadmill.

2、Download WELLFIT Fitness App, iOS version On AppStore, Android version on Google play. 

3、Open the WELLFIT app and create an account. WELLFIT app find the path "Mine - IoT services", follow network configure direction, step by step to finish the WELLFIT Treadmill network configure. 

4、Alexa controll the WELLFIT Treadmill WFTM014 order:
Alexa,Turn on the treadmill;
Alexa,Turn off the treadmill;
Alexa,Speed up;
Alexa,make it faster;
Alexa,Speed down;
Alexa,Set the speed to 5;
